kgf 0.6
language: plaintext
sources: .txt, .text, .rst, .adoc

=== lex
SKIP /[ \t]+/
TOKEN NL /\r?\n+/
TOKEN Text /[^\r\n]+/

=== grammar
Doc -> Block*
Block -> Text NL?

